These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, alhambra
There are 2 different nationalities: german, pakistani
There are 2 different favourite colors: pink, ivory
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: december, november
1. the game-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
3. the german is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Cigar       | alhambra       | game |
| Nationality         | pakistani | german  |
| Color       | ivory    | pink    |
| Birthday   | november       | december      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
2 different pets are kept: hedgehog, turtle
City: hannover, colone
The people have 2 different hobbies: hiking, baking
There are 2 different nationalities: indonesian, malaysian
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the indonesian##1
2. the person traveling to hannover is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Pet      | turtle     | hedgehog |
| City           | hannover | colone      |
| Hobby   | baking  | hiking      |
| Nationality         | indonesian | malaysian     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: december, february
2 different pets are kept: ferret, rabbit
There are 2 different favourite colors: blood-red, apricot
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: dahlia, begonia
1. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the person who's birthday is in december is the person who growsbegonia##1
3. the owner of the ferret is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Birthday      | december | february  |
| Pet          | ferret    | rabbit   |
| Color   | apricot  | blood-red   |
| Flower     | begonia     | dahlia |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
2 different games are played: canasta, scrabble
House: palace, tower
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: azalea, iris
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: handball, parkour
1. the person who's sport is handball is on the far left##1
2. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
3. the person playing scrabble is the palace house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Game      | canasta       | scrabble |
| House          | tower         | palace    |
| Flower           | iris | azalea    |
| Sport   | handball           | parkour   |

