1. the person watching sports movies is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
2. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
3. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |
| Game          | snooker | go |
| Cigar   | swisher     | ritmeester      |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | sports    |
| Sport           | lacrosse    | water-polo    |

