.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
City: new-york, liverpool
House: ranch-style, modern
There are 2 different favourite colors: white, red
There are 2 different nationalities: pakistani, mexican
1. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
2. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the mexican##1
3. the person who likes white is the person traveling to liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| City           | liverpool | new-york     |
| House   | ranch-style          | modern |
| Color           | white          | red    |
| Nationality     | mexican            | pakistani       |

 